OL,3,CHilary Benn insists 'enduring' UK-US
OL,4,Crelationship despite Trump comments
OL,6,FIran has effectively shut the vital
OL,7,Foil and gas shipping route by
OL,8,Ftargeting vessels in response to the
OL,9,FUS-Israeli air strikes.
OL,11,FMr Trump has called for countries,
OL,12,Fincluding the UK, to join a mission to
OL,13,Fprotect shipping.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
