OL,3,CHilary Benn insists 'enduring' UK-US
OL,4,Crelationship despite Trump comments
OL,6,FBut the Prime Minister, who has so far
OL,7,Fresisted the US president's demands,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We're working with all of our
OL,9,Fallies, including our European
OL,10,Fpartners, to bring together a viable
OL,11,Fcollective plan that can restore
OL,12,Ffreedom of navigation in the region as
OL,13,Fquickly as possible and ease the
OL,14,Feconomic impacts."
OL,16,FMr Trump said the UK's approach to the
OL,17,Fconflict was "terrible".
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@RO]yD@NOUyD@WO]
