OL,3,CHilary Benn insists 'enduring' UK-US
OL,4,Crelationship despite Trump comments
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Benn played down claims
OL,7,Fthat the UK has not done enough to
OL,8,Fhelp the situation and said the UK-US
OL,9,Frelationship will continue.
OL,11,FHe told UTV: "We will talk to our
OL,12,Fallies as we always do including with
OL,13,Fthe USA, with which we have close and
OL,14,Fenduring relationships, but it doesn't
OL,15,Fmean we agree on everything and that
OL,16,Fis part of a strong relationship."
OL,18,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin and Deputy
OL,19,FFirst Minister Emma Little-Pengelly
OL,20,Fare due to meet with President Trump
OL,21,Fon Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
