OL,3,CHilary Benn insists 'enduring' UK-US
OL,4,Crelationship despite Trump comments
OL,6,FDUP ministers, Communities Minister
OL,7,FGordon Lyons and Education Minister
OL,8,FPaul Givan, as well as UUP leader Jon
OL,9,FBurrows and Health Minister Mike
OL,10,FNesbitt have also travelled to take
OL,11,Fpart in meetings and engagements.
OL,13,FFor the second year in a row, Michelle
OL,14,FO'Neill has opted not to travel to
OL,15,FWashington DC for St Patrick's Day in
OL,16,Fprotest at the US policy on Gaza.
OL,18,FAlliance leader Naomi Long and SDLP
OL,19,Fleader Claire Hanna have also chosen
OL,20,Fnot to take part in the annual trip by
OL,21,Fpolitical leaders across the island.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
