OL,3,CHilary Benn insists 'enduring' UK-US
OL,4,Crelationship despite Trump comments
OL,6,FSecretary of State Hilary Benn and
OL,7,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher are
OL,8,Falso in the US capital.
OL,10,FA lunch with the Federation of Small
OL,11,FBusinesses (FSB) took place on Monday.
OL,13,FTina McKenzie from the FSB has
OL,14,Finsisted business will continue as
OL,15,Fnormal, despite the politics, during
OL,16,Fmeetings on Tuesday.
OL,18,F"I have sixteen meetings over the next
OL,19,Fthree days.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
