OL,3,CHilary Benn insists 'enduring' UK-US
OL,4,Crelationship despite Trump comments
OL,6,F"There is never a conversation about
OL,7,FSinn Fein or their position, that just
OL,8,Fdoesn't come up.
OL,10,F"We don't want to lead with people's
OL,11,Fpolitics, sometimes it may be Sinn
OL,12,FFein's, sometimes it may be the DUP's.
OL,14,F"For business people, we talk about
OL,15,Fthe opportunities for business."
